{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"526b79afad","title":"对周扬在中国作协党组扩大会上的讲话的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cbbfe11244","index":0,"year":1957,"month":11,"day":24,"articleId":"526b79afad"}],"tags":[{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9c0e44d48c","name":"周扬","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji38","name":"毛泽东全集第38卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/38-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji38":{"comments":[{"id":"61380d449f","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"526b79afad","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共中央宣传部副部长、中国作家协会党组书记周扬1957年9月16日在中国作家协会党组扩大会上所作的题为《不同的世界观，不同的道路》的讲话。这个讲话稿，根据毛泽东等的意见作了修改，于11月20日再送毛泽东审阅。这篇讲话后来发表在1958年2月28日《人民日报》，题目改为《文艺战线上的一场大辩论》。"},{"id":"12f816cbb9","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"526b79afad","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指胡乔木。"}],"contents":[{"id":"bd4c1393e6","type":"title","text":"对周扬在中国作协党组扩大会上的讲话的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"526b79afad"},{"id":"61380d449f","type":"paragraph","text":"周扬同志阅后，即送胡乔木同志转小平同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"526b79afad"},{"id":"12f816cbb9","type":"paragraph","text":"此事前日和你回顺便谈过：应印发给以小平为首的会议各同志，作一二次认真的讨论（事前细看周文），加以精密的修改，然后发表。发表前可送我看一次。会议讨论时要有周扬和其他几位文艺领导同志参加。此事请你告小平办。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"526b79afad"},{"id":"37c0e1936e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"526b79afad"},{"id":"fc7aa9bf6c","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月廿四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"526b79afad"},{"id":"c0779ae61a","type":"paragraph","text":"这是一件大事，不应等闲视之","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"526b79afad"},{"id":"b1c6d15e10","type":"paragraph","text":"我现在不看。待小平会议讨论再加修改后，我再看。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"526b79afad"}],"page":{"id":"7f4550f880","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"526b79afad","start":357,"end":357}}}},"__N_SSG":true}